{
  "stem": "8072.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the ones that remained on the truck, I didn't know where they were going.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I knew-- find out later where they were going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then the ones that got off, then they marched us to the camp, and we wound up in-- in-- in camp in a barrack.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we-- after we were there for, I don't know, that evening or that night, they had the people in charge of the barracks-- there were also prisoners, but you know, kapos and things like that.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I remember one of somebody asking that I came with my father or I came with my mother saying, do you know where they were sent?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So this one guy say, turn around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You see that chimney over there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You see that smoke over there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He said, maybe you see your mother and father coming out in that smoke.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's where they are.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They'd been in crematorium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I think that's-- that's when I found out, the first night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When they were sending you to Auschwitz-Birkenau, had you heard before of Auschwitz and Birkenau?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No-- I mean, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe some people did it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But no, I-- I didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't hear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not till I-- no, not till we got there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not until we got there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "March 14.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, it was only-- it was only a-- by truck a couple hours' ride, you know, from Krakow to--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '43.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I don't think it was that cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe it was early spring.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't-- I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- it was cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because it was still cold the next-- the following weeks while we were on camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
